## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-103">A<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent>提供物件給設計工具元件的設計主應用程式，例如[!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)]，當引發事件上控制項的設計階段檢視的特定使用者動作所造成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-103">A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent> object is provided to the designer component by the design host, for example [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], when raising an event caused by certain user actions on the design-time view of a control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-104"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件由處理<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>委派方法，會採用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>物件做為參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-104">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent?displayProperty=nameWithType> event is handled by a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate method, which takes a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object as a parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-105"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>類別是<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-105">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> class is a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>委派方法會比較<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>靜態屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent>欄位，以判斷哪一種動作引發事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate method compares the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property to the static <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent> fields to determine which type of action raised the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-107">例如，事件就會引發下列情況下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-107">For example, an event is raised under the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-108">您按一下設計介面上的區域。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-108">You click a region on the design surface.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-109">設計工具會在設計介面上的控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-109">The designer draws a control on the design surface.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-110">您輸入，或結束範本編輯模式的控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-110">You enter or exit template editing mode for a control.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-111"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>類別提供的預設委派處理<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-111">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class supplies a default delegate to handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent?displayProperty=nameWithType> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-112">自訂控制項設計工具覆寫<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>， <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A>方法來處理這些事件的設計介面上的控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-112">Custom control designers override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A> methods to process those events for the control on the design surface.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-113">設計工具主應用程式初始化<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>物件的設計介面，然後傳遞時的動作類型物件<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>委派。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-113">The designer host initializes a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object for the type of action on the design surface, and then passes the object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-114"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>物件可指出哪一種動作：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object indicates which type of action:</span></span>  
  
