-   <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-117">A<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-117">A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="78bbc-118"><xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>屬性提供事件引數所特有的動作類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="78bbc-118">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A> property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action.</span></span>  
  
